                <div class="col-lg-7">
                    <p class="lead">With the rapid growth of digital content, users face difficulty in locating accurate and relevant resources like courses, research papers, and datasets.</p>
                    <p>Traditional search engines rely mainly on keyword matching and fail to understand user intent or context. The <strong>AI Resource Finder</strong> uses Natural Language Processing (NLP) and Machine Learning (ML) to provide personalized recommendations based on:</p>
                    <ul class="list-unstyled">
                        <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle text-primary me-2"></i> User Interests & Skill Level</li>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle text-primary me-2"></i> Learning Goals & Previous Interactions</li>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle text-primary me-2"></i> Semantic Domain Context</li>
