                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-11">
                        <h4>The Challenge</h4>
                        <p>Traditional search systems provide generic results and lack personalization. Finding high-quality technical resources from scattered online platforms is time-consuming and inefficient because these systems:</p>
                        <ul class="row mt-3 list-unstyled">
                            <li class="col-md-6 mb-2"><i class="fas fa-times me-2 text-danger"></i> Do not understand user intent</li>
                            <li class="col-md-6 mb-2"><i class="fas fa-times me-2 text-danger"></i> Base results only on keyword matching</li>
                            <li class="col-md-6 mb-2"><i class="fas fa-times me-2 text-danger"></i> Provide "Information Overload"</li>
                            <li class="col-md-6 mb-2"><i class="fas fa-times me-2 text-danger"></i> Lack contextual accuracy</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
